---
import CTAButton from './CTAButton.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-slate-900/50">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Honest Pricing</h2>
      <p class="section-subheading">The only thing you pay for is the model. No subscription, no markup, no data mining.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">💰</div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">Pay OpenRouter Directly</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          You add credit to your OpenRouter account. We never touch your money.
          No markup, no platform fee, no hidden charges.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">📊</div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">Track Every Cent</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          The status bar shows tokens in/out, session cost, and remaining credit.
          You always know exactly what you're spending.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">🆓</div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">Free Models Included</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Dozens of $0 models are available (rate-limited). Try the app without
          spending a cent — then add $1 when you want premium models.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-2xl rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/20 p-6 text-center text-sm text-slate-400">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-slate-200">We're not affiliated with OpenRouter.</strong>
        We don't earn commissions, resell tokens, or track usage.
        The app costs us ~$0/month to host — we built it for privacy, not profit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>